title: 'Below Expectations'
body: I my views the product quality is below Expectations. This is doses not matches Bata's reputation.

title: 'Very tight and painful. Not fit for purpose. Do Not Buy.'
body: 'The strap is too tight. Even though I have very slim feet the slippers are very uncomfortable and painful. I cannot use them at all. My money is wasted. Not fit for purpose at all. DO NOT BUY.'

title: 'Waste of money'
body: The media could not be loaded. Very bad quality product , don't buy them ever , it will be broken under 15 days only, waste of money

title: 'Very Comfortable'
body: 'Best to use in summers and winters. Avoid using it in rainy season. It is the best overall slippers.'

title: 'Bata slippers'
body: 'Good and soft quality.. true to size.. color as shown in pic..'

title: 'Fake product'
body: 'The media could not be loaded. Fake product. Broke in just 20 days. Worst quality sleeper i have ever used.'

title: 'Good and value for money.'
body: 'The cushioning is soft and it is good for the price.'

title: 'Worthy to buy in 299'
body: 'I got real one from this dealer so its worthy to buy in rs. 299 offer'
